"'''One Step at a Time'''" is a song written by Hugh Ashley and performed by [[Brenda Lee]].  The song reached #15 on the [[Hot Country Songs|country chart]] and #43 on the [[Billboard Hot 100|''Billboard'' Hot 100]] in 1957.<ref>[http://www.musicvf.com/song.php?title=One+Step+at+a+Time+by+Brenda+Lee&id=6826 Brenda Lee, "One Step at a Time" Chart Positions] Retrieved May 3, 2014</ref>

The song was arranged by [[Jack Pleis]] and [[Al Caiola]] played guitar on the song.<ref>[http://www.45cat.com/record/930198 Brenda Lee, "One Step at a Time" single release] Retrieved May 3, 2014</ref>

